    - Term: meta/champ_2
      TermType: 0
      Languages:
      - Compete with others for 30 minutes! Rank 1st to unlock the Gold Grill Rush!
      - 在30分钟内和玩家竞争！获得第1名将会开启黄金烧烤竞速！
      - Meeding met ander vir 30 minute! Behaal die 1ste plek om die Goue Grill Stormloop oop te sluit!
